Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:02.13,Default,Fm,0,0,0,,So basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:06.27,Default,Fm,0,0,0,,that speech means we just picked a fight with the Central Nations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:08.02,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:10.28,Default,Wk,0,0,0,,As am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.63,0:00:12.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,I am too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:14.87,Default,Fm,0,0,0,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:18.16,Default,Fm,0,0,0,,From what I've heard, the speech went over well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:23.12,Default,K,0,0,0,,It inspired the serfs to reevaluate their unjust treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.87,Default,K,0,0,0,,and they're close to actually rebelling against the landowners.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:26.72,Default,Wk,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fscy100}That's precisely the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:27.92,Default,Wk,0,0,0,,Her speech
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:31.92,Default,Wk,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fscy100}has seriously shaken things up in the Southern Nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:34.10,Default,Wk,0,0,0,,The people desire independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, the question is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,how the royal family should respond.
